description: A diffident sibylla with large round glasses, who flies sagitta aboard Paraietta`s Simoun. She is Alty`s older sister, though she harbours a great hostility towards Alty as a result of their having had sexual relations in the past. Although she can be very nice, she is also alert and easily roused. She harbours an unrequited love for Paraietta.
name: Kaimu
